data.description: This renovated villa is tucked into a quiet corner of desirable Ramona Villas. This pedestrian friendly condo is close to downtown with all of its amenities! Designed by architect Richard Harrison, this condo has tile floors throughout the main living spaces and opens up to a private, enclosed backyard area that is perfect for entertaining.With generous room sizes, the home belies its square footage, living like a larger home.The kitchen features quartz countertops with shaker cabinetry, and the baths have been updated as well. There is designated covered parking with a storage locker and guest parking near. The community boasts a saltwater pool and spa and a clubhouse with fitness room, sauna, showers, tennis courts and recreation room. Be sure THIS home is on your list!!
